WEBVTT

00:00:00.226 --> 00:00:04.048
So I want to talk to you about two things tonight.

00:00:04.048 --> 00:00:06.332
Number one:

00:00:06.332 --> 00:00:09.648
Teaching surgery and doing surgery

00:00:09.648 --> 00:00:11.781
is really hard.

00:00:11.781 --> 00:00:13.365
And second,

00:00:13.365 --> 00:00:15.864
that language is one of the most profound things

00:00:15.864 --> 00:00:19.182
that separate us all over the world.

00:00:19.182 --> 00:00:21.099
And in my little corner of the world,

00:00:21.099 --> 00:00:23.049
these two things are actually related,

00:00:23.049 --> 00:00:24.981
and I want to tell you how tonight.

00:00:24.981 --> 00:00:28.987
Now, nobody wants an operation.

00:00:28.987 --> 00:00:32.926
Who here has had surgery?